(
<figureCitation id="1352BAF7FFB1FA28FDD7F970FD8555DF" box="[534,625,1704,1730]" captionStart="FIGURES 58 – 62" captionStartId="20.[151,270,1495,1519]" captionTargetBox="[193,1394,162,1465]" captionTargetId="figure@20.[151,1436,155,1471]" captionTargetPageId="20" captionText="FIGURES 58 – 62. Lophomilia spp., distribution maps. 58. L. albistria; 59. L. violescens; 60. L. striatipurpurea; 61. L. diehli; 62. L. kobesi." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/274667/files/figure.png" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
Fig. 
<number id="3DA1B455FFB1FA28FD8EF970FD8555DF" box="[591,625,1704,1730]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="60.0">60</number>
</figureCitation>
). 
<collectingCountry id="F37EE6E2FFB1FA28FD46F970FD0D55DF" box="[647,761,1704,1730]" name="Malaysia" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Malaysia</collectingCountry>
: Borneo, Sabah, Kinabalu Mt. The single specimen was collected in July (
<date id="FFD780B2FFB1FA28FEA6F917FE0555F4" box="[359,497,1743,1769]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1965-07-15">
<number id="3DA1B455FFB1FA28FEA6F917FE7155F4" box="[359,389,1743,1769]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="15.0">15</number>
.vii. 
<number id="3DA1B455FFB1FA28FE71F917FE0555F4" box="[432,497,1743,1769]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1965.0">1965</number>
</date>
). The larvae and foodplant are unknown.
</paragraph>
